    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >潜入充满敌人且极具凶险的城堡，不惜一切代价拯救公主！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Stormy Knights》中，穿上狂热骑士的盔甲，穿越大陆，拯救被怪物囚禁的公主们！置身於横向滚动的像素艺术风格中，展开策略性的即时战斗，突袭每座城堡的大厅，场景从中世纪欧洲、神秘波斯到封建的日本时代等等，还伴随着原创的復古配乐！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078670/extras/4dc46e6a64ee31fc4f00938c8ad643a7.poster.avif?t=1752073547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078670/extras/4dc46e6a64ee31fc4f00938c8ad643a7.webm?t=1752073547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078670/extras/4dc46e6a64ee31fc4f00938c8ad643a7.mp4?t=1752073547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >砍杀、闪避、防御，并击败妖精和蜥蜴人这样的小兵，一步步闯到城堡面对大魔头。如果你获得胜利，就能赢得被囚禁佳人的芳心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集宝贵的金牌在 3个技能树上购买升级，让后续的冒险更具优势。在面对看似不可能的挑战时，你能坚持这场个人征战多久呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078670/extras/bd40a63130f4dda99825df8aa1f9ff54.poster.avif?t=1752073547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078670/extras/bd40a63130f4dda99825df8aa1f9ff54.webm?t=1752073547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078670/extras/bd40a63130f4dda99825df8aa1f9ff54.mp4?t=1752073547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你的剑和盾来砍杀、躲避和阻挡敌人的攻击！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >观察敌人的战术，并在即时战斗中策略性地消灭他们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个敌人的据点面对残酷的魔头！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集金牌来购买 3 个技能树的升级。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受令人热血沸腾的復古配乐和流畅的像素艺术动画！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078670/extras/a6729fc714f92a58dcc1907244af9d52.poster.avif?t=1752073547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078670/extras/a6729fc714f92a58dcc1907244af9d52.webm?t=1752073547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078670/extras/a6729fc714f92a58dcc1907244af9d52.mp4?t=1752073547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
